Executive: Hmm.
Executive: Kis company ka naam kya hai aapka?

Executive: Tulsian.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Achcha. T U S L.
Executive: Haan samajh gaya. T U L S A N S Y A L.
Customer: Haan. T U L S E Y A L Tulsian.
Executive: Achcha inquiry nahi aa rahi hai aapko.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Achcha achcha. Sir madam main abhi dekh leta hu.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Haan ji.
